Package it.polimi.se2018.view.cli

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    CliDisplayer
    This class displays the game through the command line interface.
    CliInput
    This class gatherers the input from the user and handles it continuously through an InputEventManager that is set by the CliDisplayer.
    CliPrinter
    This class contains all the necessary print methods for the CliDisplayer and directs them to the indicated PrintStream.
    DiceSwappingManager
    Input manager used to swap a die from the draft pool with a die from the round track.
    DieIncrementManager
    Input manager used to increment or decrement a die.
    DiePlacementHandler
    Input manager used to place a die in player's pattern.
    DifficultyManager
    Input manager used to select the difficulty in single player mode.
    GameStatusHandler
    Input handler used to show the current game status.
    InputEventManager
    Abstract base class for input managers.
    LoginManager
    Input manager used to allow the player to login.
    MoveDiceManager
    Input manager used to move dice on player's pattern.
    PatternSelectionManager
    Input manager used to select a pattern among candidates.
    PrivateObjectiveManager
    Input manager used to select a private objective card among candidates.
    SelectDieManager
    Input manager used to select a die from the draft pool.
    SkipTurnHandler
    Input manager used to let the player ends its turn early.
    ToolCardConfirmManager
    Input manager used to confirm the usage of a tool card.
    ToolCardHandler
    Input manager used to select a tool card.
    ToolCardPlacementManager
    Input manager used to place a die with a tool card.
    TurnHandlingManager
    Input manager used to let the user select the available options during his turn.
    ValueAndDestinationManager
    Input manager used to select a value for a die and place it on the player's pattern.
